nodes.text: The Baxel Sector Fleet was an Imperial Sector Fleet assigned to Moff Sarn Shild of the Baxel sector during the years prior to the Galactic Civil War. The fleet was commanded by Admiral Winstel Greelanx and was mostly composed of older Imperial starships. The fleet was defeated by a smuggler fleet led by Mako Spince and Han Solo at the Battle of Nar Shaddaa in 3 BBY.
